  {{code-snippet name="content-security-policy.js"}}

  <p>You can find out more information on the CSP addon page <a href="https://github.com/rwjblue/ember-cli-content-security-policy#ember-cli-content-security-policy">here</a>. We also need to allow <code>data:</code> in <code>img-src</code> because of a <a href="https://github.com/miguelcobain/ember-paper/blob/master/app%2Fstyles%2Fpaper-button.scss">current hack</a> in paper-button.</p>

  <h2 class="md-headline">Contribution</h2>
  <p>This is a very ambitious project. Google's design specs are extensive, and non-trivial to implement. If you can port or fix a component or two, please drop a pull request or issue on GitHub or join us on slack. See README.md for more resources.</p>
  <p>With everyone's help, we can bring this amazing design spec to Ember in a modular and elegant way. The Ember way.</p>
